{
  "stem": "8233.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Why my sister didn't survive, why others didn't survive, why the little kids that I saw marching with all the men that they told me that there's not enough gas for them, that the goal that used to be [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] thrown into a-- to a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to a hall-- they're going to be burned alive.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There were all the people and children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This I could never understand because children that never-- never had the time to do anything wrong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "If I did something wrong-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "If I did, I had age already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was-- but a child, a child of two, a child of one, little children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "This upset me always.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I'm always upset by it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That's why I, really, I have to say that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But I don't mean any, any harm by it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I didn't want to have children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I promised myself when I went out that I will not bring any children to this world.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I got pregnant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm very happy now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- Rosette, back to Ravensbruck, what happened?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did you leave Ravensbruck?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left, all of us together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To, to Neustadt.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Neustadt, we would linger around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not much to do because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was-- they were liberating.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the day that we heard that they liberated us, my girlfriend came over.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said-- she said to me-- she tapped me over my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're liberated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rosette, we liberated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went and said, so what?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I cannot-- I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that's how I felt.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
